   2:				; NASCOM ROM BASIC Ver 4.7, (C) 1978 Microsoft
   3:				; Scanned from source published in 80-BUS NEWS from Vol 2, Issue 3
   4:				; (May-June 1983) to Vol 3, Issue 3 (May-June 1984)
